{
  "stem": "14867.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they came to Lvov and talked to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they insisted I should work with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was going to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I still worked with them too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and after-- and after Lvov-- oh, and then, when the Poles are winning, the Russians were winning, and Warsaw was liberated, I went to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I wanted to go as-- first of all, Warsaw was Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Lvov was Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew I wanted to get away from Ukraine, from Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wanted to go to Poland, really, to be-- in case-- after all, it was much easier for a Jew to be in Poland than in Russia.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt that way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, the Jewish organization-- and more Jews were already concentrating in Warsaw, many more.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jews who were coming back from wherever they were, they were going to Warsaw, because the Jewish population in Warsaw was much larger than any other place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and of course, they encouraged me, from the Zionist organization, I should-- I should go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also, another factor was that my cousin, when she found out that her-- her brother is alive, he sent for her to take her to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He lived in Krakow at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she already left me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I didn't have her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And before I went to Warsaw-- [SIGHS] Wait.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No, this wasn't Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "OK-- no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I came to Warsaw and worked for the organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we established an orphanage home for children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it was the Likud.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after all, without the Joint and American support, we couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because as far as the orphanage home, Americans had to help us, because we didn't have money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, some Jews came already back.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
